<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - TuFerIA</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f1a, #1a1a2e); }</style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="text-8xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400 mb-4">404</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-2">Página no encontrada</p>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">La página que buscás no existe o fue movida.</p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-xl hover:from-indigo-500 hover:to-purple-500 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/25">
      Volver al Inicio
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
